{"tid":845044,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經(???)] 空耳估歌仔","createTime":"2018-10-02T10:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T10:54:13.000Z","uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"47b2a82946662fcaeb5749d7f681e20328a4ee7f","tid":845044,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"引wiki :<br />\n空耳（日語：空耳／そらみみ）又叫誤聽。[1]空耳的本意是「幻聽」的意思，在流行文化中衍伸為對聲音（尤其語音）的再詮釋行為。<br />\n<br />\n空耳在流行用語為故意將一種語言以另一種語言的諧音重寫內容，以達到惡搞或一語雙關的目的。透過諧音改寫就好像可以「幻聽」成自己理解的語言，故在日本戲稱為「空耳」，詞彙直接沿用到華人圈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/空耳\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%A9%BA%E8%80%B3&d=6dggj3QqVcJ%2F2O%2By4evOwJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a172db7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/空耳</a>"},{"pid":"577ad6372a3f8c02b43f3ebad6cea87d77f5398c","tid":845044,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"好，我先，嚟個簡單啲<br />\n<br />\n賣呀he，賣呀who，賣呀oh<br />\n賣呀，哈哈"},{"pid":"a7e2825973f92f803c7d471c701947df6261edd5","tid":845044,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"577ad6372a3f8c02b43f3ebad6cea87d77f5398c","tid":845044,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"好，我先，嚟個簡單啲<br />\n<br />\n賣呀he，賣呀who，賣呀oh<br />\n賣呀，哈哈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"鬼佬歌 唔識呀"},{"pid":"15eb1e9b05c5961c0c4be32d017162089929709f","tid":845044,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7e2825973f92f803c7d471c701947df6261edd5","tid":845044,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"577ad6372a3f8c02b43f3ebad6cea87d77f5398c","tid":845044,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"好，我先，嚟個簡單啲<br />\n<br />\n賣呀he，賣呀who，賣呀oh<br />\n賣呀，哈哈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"鬼佬歌 唔識呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyT